WEBVTT

00:01:26.280 --> 00:01:30.416
But 30 years ago, the homicide rate
was 8.5 per hundred thousand,

00:01:30.440 --> 00:01:32.536
poverty rate was 12 percent

00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:35.736
and we emitted 35 million tons
of particulate matter

00:01:35.760 --> 00:01:38.480
and 20 million tons of sulfur dioxide.

00:01:39.400 --> 00:01:41.456
What about the world as a whole?

00:01:41.480 --> 00:01:44.896
Last year, the world had 12 ongoing wars,

00:01:44.920 --> 00:01:47.056
60 autocracies,

00:01:47.080 --> 00:01:50.696
10 percent of the world population
in extreme poverty

00:01:50.720 --> 00:01:53.696
and more than 10,000 nuclear weapons.

00:01:53.720 --> 00:01:56.216
But 30 years ago, there were 23 wars,

00:01:56.240 --> 00:01:58.136
85 autocracies,

00:01:58.160 --> 00:02:01.776
37 percent of the world population
in extreme poverty